msgctxt "6776"
msgid "おい！　酒だ！"
msgstr "Hey! It's sake!"

msgctxt "6791"
msgid "まだ飲むんかい……"
msgstr "Do you still drink ..."

msgctxt "6810"
msgid "あ～あ、何やってんだろ俺……"
msgstr "Ah, what am I doing ..."

msgctxt "6839"
msgid ""
"お前ら、これだけ一緒に飲んで騒いでも\n"
"まだ薩摩だ長州だのと言うつもりか。"
msgstr ""
"Do you guys mean that even if you drink this much together and make a noise,"
" it's still Satsuma and Choshu?"

msgctxt "6912"
msgid ""
"当たり前でしょ。\n"
"斎藤さん、アンタ俺たち長州が薩摩に\n"
"どんな目に遭わされたのか、分かってないでしょう？"
msgstr ""
"Why, of course. Saito-san, you don't know how we, Choshu, were hit by "
"Satsuma?"

msgctxt "7015"
msgid ""
"は、ケツの穴の小さいガキやで。\n"
"こんなんが頭や言うんやから長州もタカが知れとるわ。"
msgstr ""
"Is a kid with a small hole in the ass. Taka is known to Choshu from such a "
"head."

msgctxt "7098"
msgid "なんだと……"
msgstr "what……"

msgctxt "7111"
msgid "まだわからねえのか。"
msgstr "You still don't understand?"

msgctxt "7132"
msgid ""
"そんな細けぇことにこだわって、\n"
"いつまで殺し合うつもりだ。"
msgstr "Sticking to such details, I will kill each other forever."

msgctxt "7191"
msgid "そこで流れた血が、どれだけ報われたっていうんだ？"
msgstr "How much was the blood that flowed there rewarded?"

msgctxt "7245"
msgid ""
"細かいこと、か。\n"
"それをいうなら、アンタだって結構細かいことに\n"
"こだわってると思うけど？"
msgstr ""
"The details? If you say that, I think you are very particular about the "
"details, right?"

msgctxt "7335"
msgid ""
"……アイツにも同じことを言われたよ。\n"
"それよりも親っさんの遺志を継げってな……"
msgstr ""
"...... He said the same thing. Rather than that, inherit the wishes of your "
"parents ..."

msgctxt "7414"
msgid "？"
msgstr "？"

msgctxt "7417"
msgid ""
"アイツの言う通りだってことは、\n"
"分かっちゃいたんだ。\n"
"でも、俺は兄弟みたいにできちゃいねぇ。"
msgstr "I knew it was exactly what he said. But I can't do it like a brother."

msgctxt "7510"
msgid "目の前の忘れりゃあいいことを忘れられなかった。"
msgstr "I couldn't forget what I had to forget in front of me."

msgctxt "7557"
msgid ""
"……その挙句が、このザマだ。\n"
"俺は、何よりも大切なものを護れなかった。"
msgstr ""
"...... That's what this Zama is all about. I couldn't protect what was most "
"important to me."

msgctxt "7629"
msgid "兄弟？"
msgstr "brothers?"

msgctxt "7636"
msgid ""
"……土佐の武市半平太のことだ。\n"
"兄弟分なんだよ、彼らは。"
msgstr "...... It's Tosa's Takechi Hanpeita. They're siblings."

msgctxt "7693"
msgid ""
"武市半平太の兄弟分……？\n"
"そしたら、まさか……"
msgstr "Takechi Hanpeita's brothers ...? Then, no way ..."

msgctxt "7740"
msgid "言っちゃっていいのかな？"
msgstr "Can I say it?"

msgctxt "7765"
msgid ""
"……土佐勤王党の筆頭、坂本龍馬。\n"
"それがこの人の本当の名前だ。"
msgstr ""
"...... Ryoma Sakamoto, the leader of the Tosakino Party. That is the real "
"name of this person."

msgctxt "7828"
msgid "坂本龍馬？　コイツが？"
msgstr "Ryoma Sakamoto? What's this guy?"

msgctxt "7852"
msgid "この男が、坂本龍馬だ。"
msgstr "This man is Ryoma Sakamoto."

msgctxt "7876"
msgid "……どういうこっちゃ。"
msgstr "...... What kind of thing is this?"

msgctxt "7899"
msgid "？"
msgstr "？"

msgctxt "7902"
msgid "なあ、アンタ……"
msgstr "Hey, you ..."

msgctxt "7920"
msgid "人を勝手に連れまわして愚痴り倒したあげく……"
msgstr "I'll take people around and complain ..."

msgctxt "7966"
msgid "勝手に寝よった……"
msgstr "I fell asleep without permission ..."

msgctxt "7986"
msgid "坂本龍馬か……"
msgstr "Ryoma Sakamoto ..."

msgctxt "8001"
msgid "ほんと、勝手な人だね……"
msgstr "Really a selfish person ..."

